data.description: This adorable three bedroom, two bathroom home is bursting with character and ready to welcome you.  Situated in a friendly neighborhood, you'll enjoy a sense of community while being close to local parks, schools, shopping, and restaurants. This efficient layout maximizes every square foot, offering a functional kitchen, cozy bedrooms with effective use of space, two bedrooms have bed built-ins that can remain with the home or be taken out at closing.  There is a delightful sunroom and large backyard perfect to entertaining.  Schedule your showing today!
